                    (w-spg-ele-num)       not  = w-spg-alf-gat
                     go to eli-spg-att-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Decremento numero elementi in tabella           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           subtract  1                    from w-spg-ele-num          .
       eli-spg-att-999.
           exit.

